
  Snorunt    Ice Type Pokémon

  SNORUNT live in regions with 
  heavy snowfall.  In seasons without 
  snow, such as spring and summer, 
  Snorunt steals away to live 
  quietly among stalactites and 
  stalagmites deep in caverns. 
  
	Evolution Chain
      Snorunt ► Glalie

 Stage 2 Forms:
  glalie
  froslass

