 ↞---------------|ABILITIES|---------------↠

  Inner-focus:

    This Pokémon cannot flinch.

  Ice-body:

    This Pokémon heals for 1/16 
  of its maximum HP after each 
  turn during hail, and it does 
  not take hail damage regardless 
  of type.

  Moody:

    After each turn, one of this 
  Pokémon's stats at random rises 
  two stages, and another falls 
  one stage.

  If a stat is already at 6 or 
  -6 stages, it will not be chosen 
  to be increased or decreased, 
  respectively.


 Location Areas:
   Lake acuity area
   Acuity lakefront area
   Sinnoh route 216 area
   Sinnoh route 217 area
   Shoal cave b1f
